    <item>
      <title>美国对油轮的制裁影响了伊朗与中国的石油贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/iran-s-oil-trade-with-china-rattled-by-us-sanctions-on-tankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国扩大对载运伊朗原油的油轮的制裁，堵塞了伊朗原油贸易的一个关键环节，减缓了伊朗向其最有价值客户——中国——的石油输送。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/iran-s-oil-trade-with-china-rattled-by-us-sanctions-on-tankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:20:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众汽车工人因削减德国成本计划开始罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/vw-workers-start-walkouts-over-plans-to-slash-costs-in-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于工会领袖与管理层在如何削减大众汽车同名品牌的成本问题上陷入僵局，德国各地的大众汽车工人于周一发起罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/vw-workers-start-walkouts-over-plans-to-slash-costs-in-germany</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:02:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首席执行官提前离职导致 Stellantis 陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/stellantis-reels-after-ceo-s-early-departure-leaves-void</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Stellantis NV 首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯 (Carlos Tavares) 的意外离职，使得这家吉普 SUV 和标致汽车制造商在行业发生重大动荡之际失去了明确的领导层。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/stellantis-reels-after-ceo-s-early-departure-leaves-void</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:15:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞再次向巴尼耶施压，法国债券表现落后于其他债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-bonds-fall-as-le-pen-piles-pressure-on-barnier-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[极右翼政党再次威胁称，如果 2025 年预算要求得不到满足，他们将推翻法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 领导的政府。法国债券因此承压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-bonds-fall-as-le-pen-piles-pressure-on-barnier-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>野村证券在日本公司债券市场排名在调查后下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/nomura-s-japan-corporate-bond-market-rank-slips-after-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本政府加大对公司治理违规行为审查力度的背景下，野村控股公司 (Nomura Holdings Inc.) 的声誉因市场操纵丑闻而受到打击，其在公司债券市场的排名持续承压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/nomura-s-japan-corporate-bond-market-rank-slips-after-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 05:05:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价上涨，焦点是中国经济和 OPEC+ 供应会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国经济缓慢复苏迹象影响，油价和亚洲股市一同上涨，交易员们期待周四的 OPEC+ 会议找到进一步的方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 23:28:52 GMT</pubDate>
